Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真是有緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要解決鼴鼠星人之謎哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.10,0:00:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的回憶都是息息相關的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻有著成人的頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.20,0:00:22.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.89,0:00:31.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠 注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.03,0:00:40.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 我如此 三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.02,0:00:46.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線 便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.11,0:00:56.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.70,0:00:59.99,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.87,0:01:06.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.02,0:01:13.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有 Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:19.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 命中的良人就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.89,0:01:26.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠 一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.61,0:01:35.09,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠 一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和步美、元太還有光彥四個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到一個的公寓建築工地上面去打棒球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打到一半的時候棒球卻飛到隔壁別墅的院子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.32,0:01:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們跑去撿球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.91,0:01:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別墅的主人綿貫義一先生卻把我們給趕了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們回到叔叔的偵探事務所的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.46,0:01:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻碰到一個跟假面超人裡出現的鼴鼠星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得一模一樣的幸田正夫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說他的妹妹在一個月以前突然下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.51,0:02:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是被綿貫先生殺掉了然後埋在院子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望叔叔和他一起去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這樣偷偷溜進別人家的院子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自亂挖是一種違法的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生原本把希望放在叔叔身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因此生氣地回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我們想在綿貫先生到醫院檢查的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁機溜到院子裡挖掘屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在他家外面埋伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候卻又發生珠寶店被搶的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而這個歹徒竟然就是幸田正夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的真正目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.80,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼴鼠星人之謎事件〔後篇〕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼴鼠星人怎麼還沒有來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要再說鼴鼠星人好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只是長得有點像而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還是你先開始說的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的是鼴鼠星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好了 過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是不是想要挖人家的院子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我把我的鏟子借給他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等 我們看看情況再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我的推理沒有錯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你說沒有人打電話給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.96,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們醫院裡從來不因為這樣的事就打電話給病人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.01,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就奇怪了 會是誰打的電話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到米花鎮一號街 盡量快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.69,0:04:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼叫元太 我是光彥 你收到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長收到 什麼事呀光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼隊長 那個叔叔剛才坐上計程車趕回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想我們還是告訴他比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔你聽我說 綿貫先生馬上就要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要是不快點逃掉的話會被他發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說果然沒錯是什麼意思呀 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你在這裡幹什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要證明你這個傢伙做了什麼虧心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼴鼠星人被他打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你現在就給我滾出這裡 你們也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有東西發光耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是早苗的耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是玻璃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔 我來幫你打電話好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要向警方自首對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正好 我認識一個目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是目暮警官嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這裡等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼回事呀 幸田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是珠寶搶匪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.20,0:06:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我搶走的寶石都被我分散開來埋在這個院子裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.87,0:06:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說我自己也不知道寶石埋在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有請警方挖院子把它們找出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些洞是幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些都是幸田先生挖的洞呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.84,0:06:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過十幾個洞裡只有幾個埋了寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說如果不全部挖過的話是不會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底哪個洞裡埋了寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生 你該不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓警方幫你挖這個院子才搶珠寶的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說他從一開始就不打算逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實幸田先生只是希望能夠爭取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那些寶石埋在院子裡的時間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說他才會故意把一顆寶石丟在車站的樓梯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓大家以為他會坐電車逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把就是我去搶珠寶店用的模型槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你就是綿貫義一先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於你跟幸田先生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經從毛利先生那裡聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們警方現在必須把你的院子挖一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑嗎 你有什麼權力這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了調查剛才珠寶店發生的搶劫案呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就必須要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說你有什麼不可告人的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不方便讓我們把院子挖一遍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.73,0:07:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪有什麼不可告人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此 高木警官 立刻聯絡總局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪 他還笑的出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些寶石可是很小的東西 任何一個角落都不能漏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.81,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警官 我們只挖到那些寶石而己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個院子裡根本就沒有埋什麼屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.03,0:08:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不可能有那種事情的 請你再仔細的找一找好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經找得很仔細了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還要我們到什麼地方去找呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.83,0:08:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子你們已經挖的很徹底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要把這改成家庭菜園了 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管我 早苗她絕對在這個地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定被埋在這個院子裡的某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在的心情我們不是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過繼續挖下去也沒有結果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早苗 早苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生被警方逮捕歸案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他的理由是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到珠寶店去搶珠寶畢竟是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過為什麼沒有找到那個屍體呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.73,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 那是因為打從一開始就是沒有屍體呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整件事全都是幸田先生的誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.11,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 他妹妹並不是因為被綿貫先生所殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是因為別的原因才下落不明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.12,0:10:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 他的妹妹的確是被綿貫先生殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.25,0:10:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那個笑容 就是最有力的鐵證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 五月八號那天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的妹妹曾經到過這個綿貫先生的家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後又直接回去自己家裡 這個沒有錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 公司裡的同事的確是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔 你到她公司去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 你還知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要說我還問到什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是她的同事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在中午買了一些大波斯菊的種子回到公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就把種子分給了他妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大波斯菊的種子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 幸田先生不是說過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說他的妹妹最喜歡大波斯菊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.00,0:10:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說現在最有可能的就是幸田先生的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開公司之後到綿貫先生家裡之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道被什麼事情牽扯了進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從此就這樣失去了蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警政總局現在也尋著這條線開始調查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.59,0:11:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的話 柯南你還是認為那個叔叔是殺人兇手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我想應該不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是警察都沒有找到屍體呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有可能屍體不是埋在他的院子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是埋其它地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對如果這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從裡面的小路經過應該不會聽到挖土的聲音才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們到圖書館去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去圖書館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想只要查查看五月八號的報紙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定會有什麼線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我們要找的不應該是八號那天的報紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為八號晚上發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不會在八號的報紙上出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.60,0:11:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二十三號和二十四號東都百貨那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都有假面超人的節目耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要記得去看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元太你現在看的那一份是上個月的報紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那次表演我們一起去看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.24,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼對呀 你清醒一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都沒有什麼重要的新聞呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.62,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五月八號晚上到第二的天亮之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像吹了風力非常強的東風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.79,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個消息跟我們要查的案子有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子這裡沒有什麼可以當線索的新聞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.34,0:12:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想我們就去見見那個聽到挖土聲音的持田先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那都已經是一個多月前的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時我喝醉了 也記不太清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.11,0:12:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持田先生 請問你那天是從大馬路轉到小路回家的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 那天晚上這條馬路剛好在進行大的道路工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲音挺吵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我急急忙忙走進這條小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.78,0:12:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了一小段路就拿出打火機來點香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是那個時候聽到我左手邊的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有用鏟子挖土的聲音傳過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.96,0:13:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你說是這戶人家不會有錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我真的有點醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.39,0:13:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是聽到聲音從左邊傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你能不能做一下當時的樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.94,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得那個時候那個地方剛好停了一輛施工的卡車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得很檔路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就轉到這條小路來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是在這邊開始用火點煙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 這邊應該是西邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候正面是不是有很大的風吹過來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為風吹的很大 我打的火一下子就被風吹滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就轉過身把火給點上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那左邊就是右邊 右邊就是左邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.02,0:14:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 所以那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.24,0:14:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 我們就以這個鐵蓋來當本壘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知道屍體埋在什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 是我們少年偵探團發現的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到底在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問什麼問呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些小鬼八成又在那裡胡說八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔 可是新一哥哥他也說我們想得沒錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 你見到新一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有 是我剛才跟他通過電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.27,0:14:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以新一哥哥就幫我們打電話給目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 新一哥哥說要叔叔跟小蘭姐姐一起去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去 去哪裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼一回事呀 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以請你解釋一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幾個真的沒有耍我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不是有新一的電話的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是絕不會做這種事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上吧 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 我要開始說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五月八號的晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.68,0:15:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生的妹妹早苗小姐在從公司離開之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就順道來到了綿貫先生的家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著她就像幸田先生推理的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的被我們眼前的綿貫先生所殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.74,0:15:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你要說什麼昵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方昨天不是才把院子都給挖遍了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.08,0:15:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你埋藏屍體的地點其實不是這個院子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是埋在別的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快點告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妹妹被埋在什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要到了二樓 馬上就會知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快點跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.82,0:16:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 你說屍體到底被藏在這個房間的什麼地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍體不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.89,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍體就被埋在那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,案發當時這個公寓的工程就像你計劃的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行的非常順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:17:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說你把屍體埋在那裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.36,0:17:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過個幾十年都不用怕它重新翻建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你才會放心的把她埋在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有想到過了半個月的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻發生了一件意想不到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是公寓的工程竟然突然停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 那棟公寓不就蓋不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣的話那個屍體也會很快就會被發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 我一定會擔心睡不著覺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就用望遠鏡來看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也沒錯 綿貫先生除了到醫院檢查之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那天開始就幾乎整天待在家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就用這副望遠鏡每天監視公寓那塊空地上的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.61,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我根本沒有方法進入那棟公寓呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.99,0:17:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡都被包圍了 案發的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公寓的門上也都有上鎖鎖住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣說 好像你曾經調查過嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是後面還是有可疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 那個大洞是最近才發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 他到底是怎麼進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.09,0:18:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個只要問幸田先生就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來挺巧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為幸田先生剛好用了同樣的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.01,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用下水道對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.85,0:18:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天晚上因為小路入口那裡停了道路施工的工程卡車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.61,0:18:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以從馬路到卡車中間就因為道路工程形成了死角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.73,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 原來下水道可以通到這個地方來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五月八號晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為大馬路那裡在進行非常大的道路工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼用鏟子在這邊敲呀挖呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該都不會有人注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡發出的聲音有什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過不包括持田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說得沒有錯吧 綿貫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.92,0:19:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼要殺了早苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要這樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有證據嗎 不要亂冤枉人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.35,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們剛才說得這些 只不過是這個小鬼他的推理而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就算真的到這個廣場上來 那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.56,0:19:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要利用剛才那個方法不管是誰都可以到這來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.90,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且你倒是說說看屍體到底在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生的妹妹早苗小姐的遺體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這些景觀植物的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.12,0:20:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過柯南 你怎麼會知道屍體的這裡的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大波斯菊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天你妹妹就是從同事那裡分到一些大波斯菊的種子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要帶回去種的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這顆種子卻在屍體被埋的時候掉了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生根發芽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是有意殺她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天晚上她拒絕賠償我的損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就一時氣憤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.95,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣 我要中止跟你們公司的生意來往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有話好說 綿貫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,綿貫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.07,0:21:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天幸田先生妹妹的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.87,0:21:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這棵大波斯菊的幼苗下面被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.00,0:21:42.08,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.37,0:21:50.72,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此凄涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.35,0:21:58.18,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.85,0:22:07.06,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.45,0:22:15.55,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.84,0:22:24.16,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.08,0:22:33.83,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.22,0:22:42.45,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之後 幸田先生所犯下的寶石搶匪的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.05,0:22:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被法官給予緩刑的處置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.05,0:23:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.39,0:23:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還把那棵大波斯菊的花苗一起帶回了他的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.39,0:23:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說雖然我妹妹不能再回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.68,0:23:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我會把這棵花苗當成我妹妹好好的照顧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.77,0:23:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼴鼠星人之謎的案件就這樣圓滿的解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.99,0:23:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.40,0:23:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你跟新一在電話裡面說過話對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.71,0:23:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那新一現在在哪裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.29,0:23:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.63,0:23:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快回答我 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.46,0:23:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這比鼴鼠星人還恐怖耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.47,0:23:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車子來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,步美 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.23,0:24:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死石倉先生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司戶先生 就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.60,0:24:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偵探團大追擊事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.70,0:24:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.80,0:24:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!,泥坑
